name: North End one bedroom in Boston's Little Italy
description:
Stay in Boston's Little Italy. One bedroom in Boston's North End. Granite stainless appliances breakfast counter. One minute to Hanover Street, 5 minute walk to Faneuil Hall and subway.

SOFA BED MATTRESS WAS JUST REPLACED 9/2/2018

Guest access
This is not a shared space. Guests have 100% total use of the apt.

Other things to note
Laundry is on the second floor in the closet.
